cast.original_title: Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again
cast.overview: Five years after meeting her three fathers, Sophie Sheridan prepares to open her mother’s hotel. In 1979, young Donna Sheridan meets the men who each could be Sophie’s biological father.
cast.title: Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again

details.biography: Aaron Renfree was born on December 19, 1987 in Truro, Cornwall, England as Aaron Paul Renfree. He is an actor and writer, known for Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again (2018), I Dream (2004) and Vanessa White: Relationship Goals (2015).
details.name: Aaron Renfree
